三种情况均可：
1. 在 products 表的 is_imported 列和 weight 列创建复合索引，注意 is_imported 一定在最左边
2. 在 products 表的 is_imported 列和 stock 列创建复合索引，注意 is_imported 一定在最左边
3. 分别给products表的stock和weight列创建单列索引

## Index Recommendation to be Evaluated
CREATE INDEX idx_products_is_imported_stock_weight ON products(is_imported, stock, weight); Reason: Composite index - eliminates full table scan by filtering on the equality condition for is_imported followed by range conditions on stock and weight.

